<section class="header">
    <hgroup>
        <h1>Mozambique insurgency drives fears of Islamist jihad in S Africa</h1>
                            <h2> Isis claims 23 attacks in Cabo Delgado, while some say extremism product of poverty
            </h2>
            </hgroup>
    





                        
